We took a glimpse into the stylish life of Expresso-presenter, Katlego Maboe. With regards to Katlego Maboe's personal style - he was influenced by his grandfather and his late uncle who was an extraordinarily confident man who commanded attention. He wore his clothes as an extension of himself and it was a marvel to watch him walk the streets with undeniable swagger. "I believe that your style should be an extension of your personality," says Maboe. READ: Menswear embraces lace for summer "My mom instilled in me that a man's shoes are the first sign of his attention to detail. It's for that reason I have always been pedantic about my shoes - in fact sharing them is unthinkable. From my grandfather, and his endless collection of suits, I learned that a well fitted suit can elevate a man to new levels. READ: Louis Vuitton menswear Spring Summer 2017 - PICS This is something I carry with me to this day." Choose to amplify your strengths, not your weaknesses. OK.let's go! 😉 #ChooseDay A photo posted by Katlego Maboe (@katlegomaboe) on Oct 25, 2016 at 12:43am PDT G'morning fam - here's another day in your life! Take aim at your dreams. Focus.breathe...FIRE! 🙌 A photo posted by Katlego Maboe (@katlegomaboe) on Oct 10, 2016 at 10:02pm PDT A photo posted by Katlego Maboe (@katlegomaboe) on Jul 16, 2016 at 10:32am PDT E! Beyond the Red Carpet : #SAMA22 🔴 A photo posted by Katlego Maboe (@katlegomaboe) on Jun 4, 2016 at 10:42am PDT Fam, got something cool for you: A R2000 sock make-over from @nicharrystyle . Click on the link in my bio. A photo posted by Katlego Maboe (@katlegomaboe) on Feb 29, 2016 at 2:43am PST Because @gabemacht is in SA, today shall henceforth be known as #NationalSuitDay 🙌🏾🇿🇦 . 📷: @michaellegrange #iAmAClassicMan #Suit #tie #harveyspecter A photo posted by Katlego Maboe (@katlegomaboe) on Aug 31, 2015 at 7:18am PDT Just arrived in time for #ser16 A photo posted by Katlego Maboe (@katlegomaboe) on Sep 3, 2016 at 8:17am PDT #workuniform captured by @gunth